Package: mcaster1dnas
Version: @VERSION@
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libssl3 (>= 3.0.0) | libssl1.1, libxml2 (>= 2.9), libxslt1.1 (>= 1.1.34), libcurl4 (>= 7.68) | libcurl4-openssl-dev, libogg0 (>= 1.3), libvorbis0a (>= 1.3), libtheora0, libspeex1, libyaml-0-2 (>= 0.2), adduser
Recommends: ssl-cert, logrotate
Suggests: icecast2-doc
Maintainer: David St John <support@mcaster1.com>
Homepage: https://mcaster1.com/mcaster1_dnas.php
Description: Mcaster1DNAS - Digital Network Audio/Video Streaming Server
 Mcaster1DNAS is an enterprise-grade streaming media server for professional
 audio and video broadcasting. Fork of Icecast2/Icecast-KH with extensions:
 .
  - ICY 2.2 extended metadata protocol
  - YAML configuration (libyaml) alongside legacy XML
  - Per-listener SSL/TLS enforcement
  - Song history / now-playing JSON REST API (/songdata)
  - VP9/WebM video streaming support
  - Modern responsive web admin interface
  - Static mount point definitions with ICY 2.2 field support
  - Security-hardened build (stack canaries, FORTIFY, RELRO, PIE)
 .
 Supports MP3, AAC, Ogg Vorbis, Opus, FLAC, VP9/WebM, Theora, and Speex.
 .
 Homepage: https://mcaster1.com/mcaster1_dnas.php
 GitHub: https://github.com/davestj/mcaster1dnas
